message.text:
The rumors are true 🤩

Applications for the next wave of student journalists have been extended until September 16 at 11:59 PM.

From the departments of Creatives, Marketing, Production, Talents, all the way to Technicals, the doors remain open for you!🚪

Think you’ve got the courage and instinct to tell stories that matter? Sign up now at FEUNewsDotComm! ✍️

🔗: https://forms.gle/zPgVzzHEsRbwD7eB7

Caption by Elaiza Alcayde
Layout by Maria Anawen Martus 

#RoadToNDC 
#FEUNewsDotCOMM
